          Building emergent systems at the intersection of artificial intelligence,
          physics, and consciousness.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center fade-in stagger-3">
          <a href="/work" class="btn btn-primary">
            Explore My Work
          </a>
          <a href="/research" class="btn btn-outline">
            View Research
