            Building distributed intelligence systems that scale across autonomous agents and human collaboration.
          </p>
          <a href="/work#emergenthq" class="text-primary-400 hover:text-primary-300 inline-flex items-center gap-2">
            Learn more
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- AI Research -->
        <div class="glass rounded-xl p-8 hover:glow transition-all group">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">ðŸ”¬</div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 group-hover:text-primary-400 transition-colors">
            AI & Physics Research
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 mb-6">
            Exploring consciousness emergence, quantum computing applications, and the mathematical foundations of intelligence.
          </p>
          <a href="/research" class="text-primary-400 hover:text-primary-300 inline-flex items-center gap-2">
            View research
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Music Production -->
