            Composing and producing at the intersection of electronic, ambient, and experimental sound design.
          </p>
          <a href="/music" class="text-primary-400 hover:text-primary-300 inline-flex items-center gap-2">
            Listen now
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
